# Example: HTTPS for PocketBase on Jetstream (Option A in NETLIFY.md)
# 1. Point api-vizcoach.duckdns.org → 149.165.153.148
# 2. sudo apt install caddy
# 3. sudo cp deployment/Caddyfile.example /etc/caddy/Caddyfile
# 4. Edit domain, then: sudo systemctl reload caddy
# 5. PocketBase stays on 127.0.0.1:8090 (vizcoach systemd service)

api-vizcoach.duckdns.org {
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:8090
}
